text: Covid-19 has tested executives like few times in modern history. One of them is David Farr, who manages 90,000 workers world-wide as CEO of Emerson Electric. We spent much of the year with Farr to see how he guided a global conglomerate without a map. https://t.co/zgGS5FDDyq
